{"tid":1627765,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足，希望大家花少少時間睇一睇以下幾個post","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T17:57:07.000Z","uid":47541,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a7bd8deae4e5c80c614bd8d35170deb9024001b","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:40:31.000Z","msg":"各位手足，希望大家花少少時間睇一睇以下幾個post。<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得我哋既行動背後必須有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正當性</span></span></strong>，未必真係話要有規條去守，而係每個行動背後都需要有正當嘅理據。簡單講，喺「當獨裁成為事實，革命就是義務」下，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有正當性嘅目標就係政權、政權嘅工具（警察、黨鐵）</span></strong>[/size=4]；而支持政府嘅藍色公司／人（，固然係討厭，但除非佢地對我地完成目標有威脅（如攻擊手足），否則我哋亦冇必要去出擊佢地，更理想通過裝飾／罷買／和你shop作為表態，表示我方同佢地恥與為伍，但同時留有空間，歡迎佢地改邪歸正。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>［勇武和理非大和解］終極行動守則上線了</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kkRdcrW\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kkRdcrW</a><br />\n- 以武制暴唔係問題，[size=5]<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但要緊記我哋係戰鬥人員，唔係暴徒</strong></span></span>，唔好用道德直覺判斷邊個抵打，武力要用得其所。準則包括：唔好打平民（包括路過好嘈好煩、持唔同意見、但無戰鬥能力既人）、醫護人員、記者、已經投降嘅人；容許受影響嘅所有人（不論陣營）接受人道支援（包括急救）。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>經過今晚有幾樣嘢真係唔好再做</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624134\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624134</a><br />\n- 內文已經好簡結：不要成立臨時政府，提倡港獨、不要鳩打非暴力既藍絲/蝗國人、不要幫零售型藍絲/中資商店裝修<br />\n- 延伸閱讀：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>四大分類：黑裝修，紅裝飾，藍罷買，黃幫襯</strong></span></span>（<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624486）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624486）</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>梁天琦給香港人的信（29/7/19）</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1381054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1381054</a><br />\n- 唔需多解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，重申「不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不譴責」，尊重大家決定，咩都好我地都會盡力用文宣cover對外解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e7a357db37992d39274d2cdf4e622367afdfe3","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:40:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n香港人，反抗！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"953da898cb2efaec019c53393783af61200b7c32","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:41:22.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n1/20"},{"pid":"224b2985697ee827a0194406589753f86dda1618","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:41:48.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n2/20"},{"pid":"38ba08c9591213543d52dd584111fa759a23699a","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n3/20"},{"pid":"73dcae5c6e2526809e2d19598a10b8989ca98cad","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n4/20"},{"pid":"2ad4336312cccb26e0b6cff3c6b0347879a12b16","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n5/20"},{"pid":"0ec67a0345e6ed54ad95319ccda32f4a7da44e02","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n6/20"},{"pid":"acf7cdbc4b28426ce210cbb9b76b73eef087bc69","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:42:42.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n7/20"},{"pid":"7d089bbd23731e65e43954efdec83bde09ace579","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n8/20"},{"pid":"3fdf525f6295bd57151a6cc30b944b87b957db27","tid":1627765,"uid":47541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"自推20！<br />\n9/20"},{"pid":"042430a14bfc350e7e7bf4767d79570a3eee86bb","tid":16